    <i>Le Cordon Bleu College of Culinary Arts Chicago will accept CLEP proficiency or Advanced Placement (AP) tests as transfer credit for up to 12 credit hours. Tests are offered in Mathematics, English, History, Humanities, Natural Sciences, History and Social Sciences. The official transcript must be recieved prior to the start of classes.</i>
